---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Sell Your House Fast in Wichita KS | Jacob Buys Your House"
  description="Jacob Matlock buys houses for cash in Wichita KS. Fair offers in 24 hours, close in 7 days, no repairs or fees. Call (316) 816-2983."
>
  <!-- SCHEMA MARKUP -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "RealEstateAgent",
    "name": "Jacob Buys Your House",
    "description": "Local cash home buyer in Wichita, KS. We buy houses fast, as-is, for a fair price.",
    "url": "https://jacobbuysyourhouse.com",
    "telephone": "+13168162983",
    "address": {
      "@type": "PostalAddress",
      "addressLocality": "Wichita",
      "addressRegion": "KS",
      "addressCountry": "US"
    },
    "areaServed": ["Wichita", "Derby", "Mulvane", "Haysville", "Andover", "Augusta", "El Dorado"],
    "priceRange": "Fair Cash Offers",
    "openingHours": "Mo-Su 08:00-20:00"
  }
  </script>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Sell Your House Fast in Wichita, KS</h1>
      <p>Jacob Matlock is a local Wichita investor who buys houses for cash — any condition, any situation. Fair offer in 24 hours. Close in as little as 7 days.</p>
      <a href="tel:3168162983" class="btn-primary">Call (316) 816-2983</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary">Get a Cash Offer</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STEPS -->
  <section class="steps">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <div class="steps-grid">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <h3>Tell Us About Your House</h3>
          <p>Call or fill out a short form. Takes about 5 minutes. No obligation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <h3>Get a Fair Cash Offer</h3>
          <p>We'll assess your property and make a real offer within 24 hours.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <h3>You Pick the Closing Date</h3>
          <p>Need to close in 7 days? Done. Need 60 days? That works too.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">4</div>
          <h3>Walk Away With Cash</h3>
          <p>No repairs. No fees. No agents. Just cash in your hands.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SITUATIONS -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>We Buy Houses in Any Situation</h2>
      <p>There's no situation we haven't seen. Whatever's going on with your property — we can help.</p>
      <div class="situations-grid">
        <div class="situation-card">
          <h3>🏠 Inherited Property</h3>
          <p>Don't want to deal with a house you inherited? We make it simple.</p>
          <a href="/sell/inherited-house">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="situation-card">
          <h3>⚠️ Facing Foreclosure</h3>
          <p>Stop the process before it's too late. We move fast.</p>
          <a href="/sell/foreclosure">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="situation-card">
          <h3>⚖️ Going Through Divorce</h3>
          <p>Sell the house quickly and split the proceeds. Clean break.</p>
          <a href="/sell/divorce">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="situation-card">
          <h3>🔧 House Needs Repairs</h3>
          <p>Don't spend a dime fixing it. We buy as-is, period.</p>
          <a href="/sell/as-is">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="situation-card">
          <h3>🏢 Tired Landlord</h3>
          <p>Done with tenants? We buy rental properties with tenants in place.</p>
          <a href="/sell/rental-property">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="situation-card">
          <h3>💸 Behind on Taxes</h3>
          <p>Tax liens, code violations — we've handled it all before.</p>
          <a href="/sell/behind-on-taxes">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="situation-card">
          <h3>📦 Relocating</h3>
          <p>Moving for work or family? We close on your timeline.</p>
          <a href="/sell/relocating">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="situation-card">
          <h3>🏚️ Vacant Property</h3>
          <p>Empty houses cost money every month. We can take it off your hands.</p>
          <a href="/sell/vacant-house">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY JACOB -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container two-col">
      <div>
        <h2>Why Sell to Jacob?</h2>
        <p>I'm not a national hedge fund or an iBuyer algorithm. I'm Jacob Matlock — I grew up in the Wichita area, I invest here, and I care about this community.</p>
        <p>I started Pillar Home Buyers because I believe sellers deserve straight answers, a fair price, and a process that doesn't waste their time. No bait-and-switch offers. No last-minute price drops. Just honest business.</p>
        <p>If my offer doesn't work for you, I'll tell you — and I'll point you toward someone who can actually help.</p>
        <a href="/about" style="font-weight:700;color:#1a5c3a;">Meet Jacob →</a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="trust-stats" style="background:#1a5c3a;border-radius:12px;padding:40px;color:white;">
          <div class="trust-stat">
            <div class="num">3+</div>
            <div class="label">Years buying in Wichita</div>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-stat">
            <div class="num">24h</div>
            <div class="label">Cash offer turnaround</div>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-stat">
            <div class="num">7</div>
            <div class="label">Days to close if needed</div>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-stat">
            <div class="num">$0</div>
            <div class="label">Fees, commissions, or repairs</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AREAS -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Areas We Buy Houses</h2>
      <p>We buy houses throughout Wichita and the surrounding Sedgwick County area.</p>
      <div class="areas-grid">
        <a href="/areas/wichita" class="area-card">Wichita</a>
        <a href="/areas/derby" class="area-card">Derby</a>
        <a href="/areas/mulvane" class="area-card">Mulvane</a>
        <a href="/areas/haysville" class="area-card">Haysville</a>
        <a href="/areas/andover" class="area-card">Andover</a>
        <a href="/areas/augusta" class="area-card">Augusta</a>
        <a href="/areas/el-dorado" class="area-card">El Dorado</a>
        <a href="/areas/park-city" class="area-card">Park City</a>
        <a href="/areas/bel-aire" class="area-card">Bel Aire</a>
        <a href="/areas/valley-center" class="area-card">Valley Center</a>
        <a href="/areas/goddard" class="area-card">Goddard</a>
        <a href="/areas/maize" class="area-card">Maize</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="faq">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How fast can you close?</h3>
        <p>As fast as 7 days once we agree on a price. We use a local title company and handle all the paperwork. You pick the date that works for you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Do I need to make repairs or clean the house?</h3>
        <p>No. We buy houses exactly as they are. Leave whatever you don't want — furniture, trash, belongings. We handle it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Is the cash offer really fair?</h3>
        <p>We base our offers on real Wichita market data. We won't insult you with a ridiculous number. If our offer doesn't work for you, no hard feelings — we'll tell you straight.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Are there any fees or commissions?</h3>
        <p>None. You pay zero commissions, zero agent fees, and in most cases zero closing costs. What we offer is what you get.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What types of properties do you buy?</h3>
        <p>Single family homes, duplexes, multi-family, vacant lots, rental properties — if it's in the Wichita area, we're interested.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>My house is in really bad shape. Will you still buy it?</h3>
        <p>Yes. Foundation issues, roof damage, fire damage, hoarder situations — we've seen it all. Condition doesn't scare us.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="cta-block">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Get Your Cash Offer?</h2>
      <p>No obligation. No pressure. Just a straight answer from a local Wichita buyer.</p>
      <a href="tel:3168162983" class="btn-dark">Call (316) 816-2983</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
